reviewText: This is older and not as good as Unlocking the Code with Susan Sarandon but still good.  A much simpler version that does not really go into Mary Magdaline until the end and is mostly the Arthur legend that is all about the cup.

I was expecting more from this History Channel's Holy Grail but the information are not much different from what you hear from Da Vinci Code's echo documentaries. This is a very brief documentary and the quality is not that good.
